    "usage_text":       "● Navigation\n  • Next: Right or Space\n  • Previous: Left or Backspace\n  • First: Home, Last: End\n\n● Zoom\n  • F: Fit to window, 1: Actual size (1:1), W: Fit to width\n  • Ctrl + Mouse Wheel: Zoom in/out\n\n● View Toggles\n  • F11: Fullscreen\n  • N: Folder explorer toggle\n  • I: Overlay toggle\n  • M: Metadata panel toggle\n  • T: Thumbnail bar toggle\n  • S: Status bar toggle\n  • F12: Performance overlay toggle\n\n● File Operations\n  • Ctrl+O: Open file\n  • Ctrl+Shift+O: Open folder\n  • F2: Rename\n  • Ctrl+X/C/V: Cut/Copy/Paste\n  • Delete: Delete\n  • Ctrl+Shift+E: Open file location\n  • Alt+Enter: Properties\n  • Ctrl+Shift+A: Copy file path\n  • Ctrl+Shift+I: Copy image to clipboard\n\n● Highlight\n  • H: Toggle highlight\n  • Ctrl+Shift+H: Clear all highlights\n  • Ctrl+Shift+Delete: Delete highlighted files\n  • Ctrl+Shift+C: Copy highlighted files\n  • Ctrl+Shift+X: Cut highlighted files\n\n● Rotate\n  • Ctrl+Shift+Left: Rotate left\n  • Ctrl+Shift+Right: Rotate right\n  • Ctrl+Shift+Up: Reset rotation\n  • Ctrl+Shift+Down: Apply rotation\n\n● Capture\n  • Ctrl+Alt+C: Capture screen to clipboard\n  • Ctrl+Alt+S: Capture screen to file\n\n● Print\n  • Ctrl+P: Print current image\n  • Ctrl+Alt+P: Print all images\n  • Ctrl+Shift+P: Print highlighted images\n\n● Misc\n  • Ctrl+G: GPS map\n  • Ctrl+,: Settings\n  • F1: About\n  • F4: System information\n  • F5: Refresh current image\n  • E: Enter edit mode",
